クラス StatusEffectsObject

java.lang.Object
xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.shared.SharedObject
xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.shared.StatusEffectsObject
public class StatusEffectsObject extends SharedObject
Specifies multiple applied status effects. Only a single EffectObject can be mapped to a single Effect.
